This is the Nipah Virus Inhibitor Knowledgebase (NVIK) source code for publication.

It is hosted at http://bioinfo.imtech.res.in/anshu/nipah

The NVIK is developed using the open source LAMP (Linux-Apache-Mysql-PHP) server technology. We have used PHP, HTML, JavaScript, AJAX, CSS, and Open Babel.
The web-interface has provision for text, structure, and complex query based search and other options for browsing.

You can download and use the NVIK Virtual Machine (VM) in VirtualBox with all soruce code and environment settings.
Please visit bioinfo.imtech.res.in/anshu/nipah/vbox.php

Please cite as:
bioRxiv preprint doi: https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.03.12.977918
